></span>: <span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">20</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">명</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">5. </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">지원 자격</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">- 2026-1</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">학기 재학생으로서 상기 지역 주소지 또는 해당지역 출신고교 재학생</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">- </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">불교동아리 부원 또는 가입 예정인 학생</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">6. </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">신청 방법</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">- n-DRIMS</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">접속</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">→</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">왼쪽상단</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">→</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;